select fiscal_year year , gl.period period , cast(gl.company as varchar) entity , acct_level01 account , sum(amount) amount from dbo.dw_gl_transactions gl with (nolock) join dbo.dw_gl_account acct with (nolock) on gl.acct_key = acct.acct_key join dbo.dw_gl_org org with (nolock) on org.org_key = gl.org_key left join [dbo].[DW_GL_EIS_EO] eo with (nolock) on eo.account = acct_level01 and eo.level_3 = org.[Level3_Level_Code] and eo.[GBR_Account] = acct.[GBR_Account] where (gl.company like '933%' or gl.company = '9326' or gl.company = '9360') and period = $$CY_MONTH_NUM and fiscal_year = $$FISCAL_YEAR and scenario = 'Actual' and currency_type = 'BASE' and acct.[GBR_Account] <> 'OPER_EXPENSE' group by fiscal_year , period , gl.company , acct_level01
union all
select fiscal_year year , gl.period period , cast(gl.company as varchar) entity , acct_level01 account , sum(amount) amount from
dbo.dw_gl_transactions gl with (nolock) join dbo.dw_gl_account acct with (nolock) on gl.acct_key = acct.acct_key join dbo.dw_gl_org org with (nolock) on org.org_key = gl.org_key left join [dbo].[DW_GL_EIS_EO] eo with (nolock) on eo.account = acct_level01 and eo.level_3 = org.[Level3_Level_Code] and eo.[GBR_Account] = acct.[GBR_Account] where (gl.company like '933%' or gl.company = '9326' or gl.company = '9360') and period = $$CY_MONTH_NUM and fiscal_year = $$FISCAL_YEAR and scenario = 'Actual' and currency_type = 'BASE' and acct.[GBR_Account] = 'OPER_EXPENSE' and eo_summary_line = 'I8.24' group by fiscal_year , period , gl.company , acct_level01

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
select fiscal_year ,fiscal_period, case when upper(trim(brand_name ))= 'UNMAPPED' then 'GEAR FOR SPORTS' else upper(trim(brand_name )) end brand_name, gm.sales_measure_name measure_name , sum(dollars) amount from slba.gross_margin_style_account gm join style_master_1 sm on gm.style_num = sm.style_num and lower( trim(sm.division_group)) = 'gfs' where upper(trim(slba_division_code)) = 'GF' and fiscal_year =$$FISCAL_YEAR and fiscal_period = $$CY_MONTH_NUM and upper(trim(gross_margin_ind)) = 'Y' and gm.UPDATE_USERID <> 'LawPlugGFSETL' group by case when upper(trim(brand_name ))= 'UNMAPPED' then 'GEAR FOR SPORTS' else upper(trim(brand_name )) end , gm.sales_measure_name , fiscal_period , fiscal_year having sum(dollars) <> 0
union all
select fiscal_year , fiscal_period , case when upper(trim(brand_name ))= 'UNMAPPED' then 'GEAR FOR SPORTS' else upper(trim(brand_name )) end as brand_name , gm.cost_measure_name, sum(extended_cost_dollars) from slba.gross_margin_style_account gm join style_master_1 sm on gm.style_num = sm.style_num and lower( trim(sm.division_group)) = 'gfs' where upper(trim(slba_division_code)) = 'GF' and fiscal_year =$$FISCAL_YEAR and fiscal_period = $$CY_MONTH_NUM and upper(trim(gross_margin_ind)) = 'Y' and gm.UPDATE_USERID <> 'LawPlugGFSETL' group by case when upper(trim(brand_name ))= 'UNMAPPED' then 'GEAR FOR SPORTS' else upper(trim(brand_name )) end , gm.cost_measure_name , fiscal_period , fiscal_year having sum(extended_cost_dollars) <> 0
